FuncDef: The reset aaa statistics access-type-authenreq command clears the number of requesting for authentication. The reset aaa statistics access-type-authenreq command clears the number of requesting for authentication. This command is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K and CE6820S.
